    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2 submissions. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. Decision: Accepted for the stated intended use.",
